      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EXTRA VOLTAGE (8) is a classy type in the money every start so far, scoring at this track (18.63) last time and making it two straight wins. Tends to go well on this box draw. Rates highly here and will go close. BERNARDO BLUE (1) finds it hard to win but has a consistent overall record, having placed eight of 14 career runs. Continues to race well, filling the minors at the last three starts, the latest when second (19.11) at this track. Solid record here winning two races. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Overdue and is among the main hopes. HOLD THE GAVEL (7) boasts a strong record this journey with nine wins and two minors from 15 tries. Recorded a half a length win (19.08) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. Can feature in the finish. HEY ERNIE (5) was strongly fancied but finished second last time (18.67) at this track, bringing a three-run winning streak to an end. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely.",
